cs.NE, cs.DC, cs.OH, cs.CE, cs.LG

The paper proposes a novel Divide-and-Conquer (DC) based EA for large-scale optimization problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also extensively discusses the DC approach, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of parallel computing, which could place it in cs.OH (Other Computer Science) or cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Finally, the paper proposes a new algorithm, which could also place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning).
